Usage: reset_sense [-help] [-all  | [[-clocks <clock_list>] <pin_or_port_list>]]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<pin_or_port_list>     # List or collection of pins or ports for which the
                       # clock sense constraints will be removed
                       # (string, required)
-all                   # Resets all the specified clock_sense constraints
                       # (bool, optional)
-clocks <clock_list>   # List of clocks for which the clock sense constraints
                       # are to be removed (string, optional)